These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, mexican
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, emerald
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Color         | emerald | amber    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Sport   | cricket | badminton  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, whist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Game         | scrabble   | whist  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
City: berlin, miami
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| City     | miami       | berlin      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different pets are kept: goat, pony
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Pet        | goat      | pony  |
| Sport       | rugby     | cricket    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

